U.K. Stocks Rally as U.S. Jobs Growth Tops Forecasts; BP Shares Advance

-- B y   A d a m   H a i g h
-- 
2011-10-07T12:33:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/u-k-stocks-rally-as-u-s-jobs-growth-tops-forecasts-bp-shares-advance.html
U.K. stocks rallied after a report
showed employers in the U.S. added more payrolls than forecast
last month. The benchmark FTSE 100 Index climbed 54.77, or 1.1
percent, to 5,346.03 as of 1:31 p.m. in  London .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
